comments: Beverley (LAC) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) leg while he is in his shooting motion.
Harden (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by George (LAC).
Green (LAC) brings his arm forward and makes contact with the ball on Capela's (HOU) initial shot attempt.
Green's (LAC) arm is positioned around Capela's (HOU) back, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his shot attempt at the rim.
Coach Rivers (LAC) steps onto the court and signals for a timeout, but the timeout is not granted by officials on the floor.
Leonard (LAC) is in a legal picking position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Rivers (HOU).

As Westbrook (HOU) is attempting to gather the ball, Williams (LAC) gets his hand on the ball and dislodges it from Westbrook.  Westbrook then legally takes a dribble after regaining possession of the ball.
Tucker (HOU) receives the pass with his left foot out of bounds.
The shot is imminent when Capela (HOU) is in the lane for three seconds.
Harrell (LAC) makes marginal contact with Tucker (HOU) during the shot attempt near the rim.
Leonard (LAC) is in a legal picking position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Rivers (HOU).
George (LAC) remains in bounds when he receives the pass.
Westbrook (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by George (LAC).
Williams (LAC) absorbs the contact to the body from Capela (HOU) and Green (LAC) cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) maintains his pivot foot when he gathers the ball.
Leonard (LAC) releases from contact with Tucker (HOU) at the end of his drive.
Leonard (LAC) reaches in and makes contact to the body of Harden (HOU) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (LAC) engages with Tucker (HOU) during the made free throw.  The level of contact is not consistent with Tucker's reaction.
Tucker (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Leonard (LAC).
Green (LAC) dislodges Harden (HOU) from his rebounding position.
Williams (LAC) and Capela (HOU) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Westbrook (HOU) commits a take foul on George (LAC).
Harden (HOU) disengages from the contact with Leonard (LAC) before receiving the pass.
George (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Harden (HOU).
